          14
        ]
      ],
      "details": {}
    },
    {
      "review_id": "rJldfOy-27",
      "rebuttal_id": "ryezm5-70X",
      "sentence_index": 38,
      "text": "Thus, this information is brought into the model by considering the posterior distribution for the network, where the prior models the degrees of the nodes, or the block structure.",
